thor TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.794</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:334\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.334</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:415\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.415</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:9:191\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.191</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:18:524\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.524</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"c\" id=\"n74626.5\" level=\"4\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> in orat. obliq., <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg001.perseus-grc1:824\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Tr.\">Tr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">824</biblScope> </bibl> (lyr.), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg006.perseus-grc1:4:6:20\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ An.\">An.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.6.20</biblScope> </bibl> ; in implied orat. obliq., <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:24:344\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">24.344</biblScope> </bibl> (of a past promise) ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀποδοτέον . . ὁ. μανεὶς ἀπαιτοῖ</foreign> we were not [as you remember] to . . , <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg030.perseus-grc1:332a\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ R.\">R.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">332a</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"d\" id=\"n74626.6\" level=\"4\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> where the principal clause has an opt., <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">μηδ᾽ ἀντιάσειας ἐκείνῳ ὁππότε νοστήσειε</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:18:148\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.148</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg030.perseus-grc1:396c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ R.\">R.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">396c</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg007.perseus-grc1:1:6:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Cyr.\">Cyr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.6.3</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n74626.7\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> in indirect questions, with ind., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἦ ῥά τι ἴδμεν . . ὁππότε Τηλέμαχος νεῖται</foreign>; <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">when</tr_> he is to return, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:4:633\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.633</biblScope> </bibl> ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εἰς ὁ.</quote_> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">by what time,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0026.tlg003.perseus-grc1:99\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aeschin.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.99</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> : rarely after a past tense, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">προσεδέρκετο, δέγμενος αἰεί, ὁππότε δὴ . . ἐφήσει</foreign> (for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐφείη,</foreign> <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">v.</abbr> supr. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0026.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.2</biblScope> </bibl> b) <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:20:386\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">20.386</biblScope> </bibl> ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εἰς σὲ βλέψαι καὶ τὸν ταμίαν ὁπότ᾽ ἄριστον παραθήσει</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg004.perseus-grc1:613\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ V.\">V.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">613</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=\"n74626.8\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὁποτεοῦν</quote_> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">at any time whatever,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg025.perseus-grc1:1049a:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Metaph.\">Metaph.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1049a1</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"B\" id=\"n74626.9\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> in causal sense, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">because, since,</tr_> with ind., <bibl n=\"Thgn. 749\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\